hom he equally abhors. Yet a small child, Cindy Lou Who, decides to try befriend the Grinch.','NULL'),(9257,'S.W.A.T.',117,'2003-08-08','English',5.70,170,'An imprisoned drug kingpin offers a huge cash reward to anyone that can break him out of police custody and only the LAPD\'s Special Weapons and Tactics team can prevent it.','NULL'),(9339,'Click',107,'2006-06-22','English',5.90,441,'A workaholic architect finds a universal remote that allows him to fast-forward and rewind to different parts of his life. Complications arise when the remote starts to overrule his choices.','NULL'),(9361,'The Last of the Mohicans',112,'1992-09-25','English',6.40,139,'As the English and French soldiers battle for control of the North American colonies in the 18th century, the settlers and native Americans are forced to take sides. Cora and her sister Alice unwittingly walk into trouble but are saved by Hawkeye, an orphaned settler adopted by the last of the Mohicans.','NULL'),(9381,'Babylon A.D.',101,'2008-08-29','English',5.50,168,'In Babylon A.D Vin Diesel stars as a veteran-turned-mercenary who is hired to deliver a package from the ravages of post-apocalyptic Eastern Europe to a destination in the teeming megalopolis of New York City. The \"package\" is a mysterious young woman with a secret.','NULL'),(9473,'South Park: Bigger, Longer & Uncut',81,'1999-06-30','English',6.80,182,'When the four boys see an R-rated movie featuring Canadians Terrance and Philip, they are pronounced \"corrupted\", and their parents pressure the United States to wage war against Canada.','NULL'),(9506,'Anger Management',106,'2003-03-05','English',5.70,140,'After a misunderstanding aboard an airplane that escalates out of control, the mild-mannered Dave Buznik is ordered by Judge Daniels to attend anger management sessions run by Doctor Buddy Rydell, which are filled with highly eccentric and volatile men and women. Buddy\'s unorthodox approach to therapy is confrontational and abrasive and Dave is bew